We use herein a 15-year historical record (1995–2010) of monthly demand data (D), and reservoir inflow (Q
in) and outflow (Q
out) rates of the Melbourne area. As the available demand data does not distinguish among the four main contributing reservoirs (Maroondah, O’Shannassy, Upper Yarra, and Thomson) we simulate their combined storage with Equation 1 using cumulative values of their inflow rates. The initial and maximum reservoir storage are set to S
